WEBVTT

00:00:59.906 --> 00:01:02.275
Cfare ndodh kur sheqeri prek gjuhen tone?

00:01:02.275 --> 00:01:03.528
A eshte e vertete se po te hash pak sheqer

00:01:03.528 --> 00:01:05.480
deshiron edhe me shume?

00:01:05.480 --> 00:01:07.025
Kafshon nje shufer grunjerash.

00:01:07.025 --> 00:01:08.276
Sheqeri qe ajo permban

00:01:08.276 --> 00:01:10.528
aktivizon receptoret e shijet

00:01:10.528 --> 00:01:12.770
qe ndodhen ne gjuhe.

00:01:12.770 --> 00:01:15.771
Keta receptore dergojne nje sinjal ne trungun e trurit,

00:01:15.771 --> 00:01:17.375
dhe nga aty, sinjali shperndahet

00:01:17.375 --> 00:01:19.261
ne zona te ndryshme te trurit,

00:01:19.261 --> 00:01:21.813
njera prej te cilave eshte korteksi.

00:01:21.813 --> 00:01:23.964
Zona te ndryshme te kortekstit

00:01:23.964 --> 00:01:25.864
perpunojne shije te ndryshme:

00:01:25.864 --> 00:01:26.399
te hidhuren,

00:01:26.399 --> 00:01:26.985
te kripuren,

00:01:26.985 --> 00:01:27.711
umamin,

00:01:27.711 --> 00:01:29.823
dhe ne rastin tone, te emblen.

00:01:29.823 --> 00:01:31.328
Prej ketej sinjali aktivizon